Name: DogFight
About the game: DogFight is a VR experience interactive entertainment application where the aim is to keep shooting down enemy planes before they destroy the allied boat. Your job is to protect the boat from enemy kamikaze fighter planes. You can play as the fighter pilot with first-person view of the pilot.
